org.eclipse.modisco.manifest
Interface Bundle

public interface Bundle

A representation of the model object 'Bundle'.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Singleton
  • Symbolic Name
  • Version
  • Activator
  • Activation Policy
  • Required Execution Environment
  • Vendor
  • Required Bundles
  • Imported Packages

See Also:
